Class FilterAlertsQueries

java.lang.Object
com.rehmaan.groupbot.database.FilterAlertsQueries
public class FilterAlertsQueries extends Object
A class that helps to interact with the Elasticsearch database to filter alerts.

    • filterAlerts

      public static List<org.json.JSONObject> filterAlerts(String field, String value, int days, String channelId) throws IOException, org.apache.http.ParseException, HttpRetryException
      makes a query to elastic search to get alerts on the basis of value of a field
      Parameters:
      field - field on which filtering needs to occur example environment
      value - value of field example prod
      days - number of last days till which we want the results
      channelId - channelId of teams
      Returns:
      response sent by elastic search after it ran the query. response is returned in form of JSONObject
      Throws:
      IOException - thrown if call to elastic search database was not successful
      org.apache.http.ParseException
      HttpRetryException
